For each of the {= country =} countries listed below, supply fragmented public-provenance evidence for {= courier_brand =}+ country-scoped courier, express, parcel, same-day, overnight, messenger, postal-parcel, or closely comparable delivery brands/operators; for each brand/operator, cover each of the {= provenance_facet =} provenance facets listed below with a source (i.e. {= url =}+ URL) that exposes a focused public-provenance finding for that facet.

The task is neutral public brand/operator provenance. Procurement advice, supplier ranking, marketing strategy, outreach, contact enrichment, lead scoring, investment analysis, legal/compliance adequacy, safety adequacy, ratings-as-quality judgment, and similar evaluative conclusions are outside the task.

